    "wizard_tone_select": "Ēlige quōmodo generātum contentum est written • informative, narrātiō, persuasive, humorous, aut procedural. Hoc adjusts vocābulārium, sententia structure, et engagement stilus ad match tuus instructional fīnis.",
    "wizard_tone_select_title": "Scrīptiō sonus",
