    "wizard_dok_select": "Pōne Webb's altitūdō Knowledge gradus. gradus 1 (recall) ūtitur simplex fact-based contentum. gradus 4 (extended thinking) creat complexus textus requiring synthesis et analysis.",
    "wizard_dok_select_title": "altitūdō Knowledge",
