      "educational_concepts": "💡 Conceptus educativi",
      "color_theory_additive_vs_subtractive_m": "Theoria colorum (mixtura additiva vs subtractiva, colores complementarii, HSL/RGB), curvae mathematicae (hypotrochoides, Lissajous), fractalia et autosimilitudo, geometria tessellationis, perceptio visualis op art, normae accessibilitatis WCAG et ars computatoria. Quodque instrumentum docet mathematicam post pulchritudinem.",
